item.title: CVE-2021-34633|2024-09-16T16:58:21.114Z -- youtube%20feeder -- youtube%20feeder
item.description: The Youtube Feeder WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Cross-Site Request Forgery via the printAdminPage function found in the ~/youtube-feeder.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 2.0.1.
